=Description=

"The Rebel Roo will work to circulate tactics, ideas, grievances, desires and demands, as well as supporting the development of national (and eventually transnational) organisation.

The growth of the ‘gig economy’ is part of a new direction in the organisation of the labour process enabled by new developments in mobile technology and the destruction of the social settlement won by the labour movement under social democracy. Deliveroo is one of the most prominent examples of these ongoing changes in the political and technical conditions of exploitation, and it is vitally important that workers get a handle on how to exert power in this new composition."
(https://www.weareplanc.org/blog/a-new-initiative-rebel-roo-1/)

